## Summary
This documentation page explains how to test guides and surveys in Amplitude using Preview mode, which allows developers to verify conditions, settings, and behavior before launching. It covers entering preview mode, understanding condition statuses (trigger, limit, throttle), troubleshooting preview issues, and conducting live testing with targeted cohorts.

